data.description: This exceptional 5 bedroom/4 bath property offers a truly move-in ready experience, with all the features and upgrades you could ever dream of. This floorplan is a must see with 2 primary suites! Boasting a better-than-new condition with all the expensive new construction items already done, this home has been meticulously maintained and thoughtfully enhanced, ensuring a comfortable and stylish living environment for its lucky new owners. Step inside and be greeted by the spacious and inviting atmosphere that permeates throughout this stunning residence. The open-concept floor plan seamlessly blends the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating a perfect setting for entertaining friends and family. The abundance of natural light that floods in through the large windows creates an uplifting ambiance, further enhancing the charm of this delightful home.The well-appointed kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring modern appliances, ample storage space, and sleek countertops that perfectly complement the contemporary design. The adjacent dining area offers a convenient space for enjoying meals with loved ones while relishing in the captivating views of the surrounding landscape.With five bedrooms, this home provides an abundance of space for a growing family or guests. The primary suite is a true retreat, complete with a luxurious ensuite bathroom and a walk-in closet, providing a serene sanctuary to unwind and recharge.One of the standout features of this property is the presence of solar panels, providing eco-friendly and cost-effective energy solutions. Embrace sustainable living while enjoying the benefits of reduced utility bills and a smaller carbon footprint. The landscaping has been meticulously designed and executed, creating a serene oasis that seamlessly blends with the natural surroundings. Enjoy the peace and tranquility of a suburban lifestyle while still being within easy reach of city conveniences. All appliances with the oversized washer & dryer included!
